But it's not something I'm a specialist of, so I don't know if I can provide a much better answer than this.

02:10:28.450 --> 02:10:35.450
Maybe DuckDB, but I know that there is work being done for doing the computation directly inside the database.

02:10:35.450 --> 02:10:43.450
So you don't need to bring it inside our memory and you can still do this analysis on your full data set.

02:10:44.450 --> 02:10:50.450
